<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>BasketHub - Encontre Quadras de Basketball</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --orange-primary: #FF8C00;
      --orange-dark: #E67E00;
      --orange-light: #FFB84D;
      --dark-bg: #0F1419;
      --card-bg: #1A1F2E;
      --text-light: #E0E0E0;
      --text-muted: #A0A0A0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--dark-bg);
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange-primary) 0%, var(--orange-dark) 100%);
      padding: 1rem 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .header-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .logo::before {
      content: "🏀";
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, #1a2a3a 100%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-30px); }
    }

    .hero-content {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 800px;
      z-index: 10;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange-light) 0%, var(--orange-primary) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      animation: slideDown 0.8s ease;
    }

    @keyframes slideDown {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: slideDown 0.8s ease 0.2s both;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      animation: slideDown 0.8s ease 0.4s both;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange-primary) 0%, var(--orange-dark) 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--orange-primary);
      border: 2px solid var(--orange-primary);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--orange-primary);
      color: white;
    }

    
    .features {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: -100px auto 0;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 20;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      border-color: var(--orange-primary);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      color: var(--orange-light);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    /* Quadras Section */
    .quadras-section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 4rem auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .section-title span {
      color: var(--orange-primary);
    }

    .quadras-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .quadra-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: 15px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .quadra-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.3);
      border-color: var(--orange-primary);
    }

    .quadra-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange-primary), var(--orange-dark));
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 4rem;
    }

    .quadra-info {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .quadra-info h3 {
      color: var(--orange-light);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .quadra-info p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .stars {
      color: var(--orange-primary);
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    
    .cta-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange-primary) 0%, var(--orange-dark) 100%);
      margin: 4rem 0;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .cta-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background: #0a0e14;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.1);
    }

    footer p {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .hero-content p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .cta-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      nav {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero::before, .hero::after {
        display: none;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="header-container">
      <div class="logo">BasketHub</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#footer" onclick="window.location.href='#footer'">Sobre</a>
        <a href="#login" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Login</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Encontre Seu Próximo Jogo</h1>
      <p>Conecte-se com apaixonados por basketball, compartilhe informações de quadras e organize partidas na sua região</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Explorar Quadras</button>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary">Saber Mais</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  
  <section id="features" class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📍</div>
      <h3>Encontre Quadras</h3>
      <p>Descubra as melhores quadras de basketball perto de você com localização e endereço precisos</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📸</div>
      <h3>Fotos Reais</h3>
      <p>Veja fotos de alta qualidade das quadras, pisos, iluminação e toda infraestrutura disponível</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">⭐</div>
      <h3>Avaliações</h3>
      <p>Leia avaliações e classificações de outros jogadores sobre a qualidade e experiência em cada quadra</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">👥</div>
      <h3>Faça Amigos</h3>
      <p>Conecte-se com outros jogadores, organize partidas e crie uma comunidade de basketball</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
      <h3>Organize Partidas</h3>
      <p>Publique partidas planejadas, convide amigos e reúna a galera para jogos incríveis</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
      <h3>App Intuitivo</h3>
      <p>Interface simples e fácil de usar para encontrar informações sobre quadras em poucos cliques</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Pronto para Jogar?</h2>
      <p>Junte-se à nossa comunidade de basketball e comece a explorar as melhores quadras agora</p>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Começar Agora</button>
    </section>
  </div>

  
  <footer id="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2026 BasketHub - Seu lugar para encontrar quadras de basketball</p>
    <p>Criado para apaixonados por basketball</p>
  </footer>
  <h1>Pub/Sub Rails</h1>

  <div id="messages"></div>
</body>
</html>